# Tuck In App - Project Structure

## Key Files

- [app/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/_layout.tsx) - Root layout with WindDownProvider
- [app/(tabs)/index.tsx](mdc:app/(tabs)/index.tsx) - Home screen with schedule timeline
- [app/winddown-routine.tsx](mdc:app/winddown-routine.tsx) - Wind-down routine configuration
- [contexts/WindDownContext.tsx](mdc:contexts/WindDownContext.tsx) - Routine state management
- [lib/supabase.ts](mdc:lib/supabase.ts) - Supabase client configuration

## Wind-Down Routine System

The wind-down routine is managed through:
1. **Context**: [contexts/WindDownContext.tsx](mdc:contexts/WindDownContext.tsx) stores routine items
2. **Configuration Screen**: [app/winddown-routine.tsx](mdc:app/winddown-routine.tsx) allows users to customize
3. **Home Screen**: [app/(tabs)/index.tsx](mdc:app/(tabs)/index.tsx) displays the schedule timeline
4. **Wind-Down Flow**: [app/winddown.tsx](mdc:app/winddown.tsx) guides users through enabled items

## Important Notes

- Routine items have `duration` and `description` properties
- Timing is automatically adjusted when items are reordered
- Validation prevents overlapping times
- Items are sorted by `order` field for display
